data.description: ***BACK ON MARKET NEW ROOF, NEW CARPET NEW TILE FLOORING****Welcome home 1818 Opal Peach in the gated community of Sterling Lakes-Country Living at it best-easy commute to medical center or to Dow-this home features updated floors on 1st floor-deck added to back-interior recently painted-open floor plan-utility area upstairs with the bedrooms-split floor plan on bedrooms-large primary with walk in closet-primary bath has large soaking tub/separate shower with glass door-2nd bathroom has tub shower combo-3rd bedroom is being used as a media room-huge backyard large enough to make your very own oasis-walking distance to the elementary school-no back neighbors-community has many amenities including 2 pools, splash pad and kiddy pool-5 min from the new Manvel town center that will feature the newest H E B super store and numerous other stores and restaurants opening 2023-call today for your private showing
